<p>Point of clarification&#8230;</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Borderline&nbsp;Spoiler&nbsp;Alert!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Close</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Glacon hasn't gone crazy necessarily. He's just exhaustively broken down a containment breach into a base line risk-assessment that he believes he can control and revert by exploiting Crom to get by AI restricted security/safety controls. From his perspective, it's a harmless white lie to save his own skin and turn him into a hero.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>More to come! :)</p>

